could get ahead of the data game.

00:03:39.700 --> 00:03:44.740
And really move the differentiator away
from being price competition around

00:03:44.740 --> 00:03:49.420
voice to being data services that our
consumers would value and that would

00:03:49.420 --> 00:03:53.680
provide some stickiness that would
