We've seen already a lot of
things that I might be repeating,

00:23:44.570 --> 00:23:49.940
but I'll try to add the world view to
this in terms of what we see in mobile

00:23:49.940 --> 00:23:53.290
media from the holistic perspective.

00:23:53.340 --> 00:23:55.500
To start off,
my name again is Eugene Sarmiento.

00:23:55.500 --> 00:23:58.500
I'm a Product Marketing Manager for
Ericsson.

00:23:58.560 --> 00:24:02.300
I've been working with the streaming
and download solution from Ericsson

00:24:02.300 --> 00:24:08.300
for the past two and a half years,
working with the global operators,

00:24:08.410 --> 00:24:09.800
trying to push them.

00:24:10.140 --> 00:24:13.100
towards this mobile
and media convergence.

00:24:13.380 --> 00:24:17.340
Now,
the slides I'm about to present to you,

00:24:18.660 --> 00:24:21.630
We'll mainly cover three main areas.

00:24:21.770 --> 00:24:25.800
First of all, what opportunities we see
in the mobile media space,

00:24:25.800 --> 00:24:29.700
what's Ericsson's role in this space,
and finally,

00:24:29.700 --> 00:24:34.960
what are the key success factors that
will basically take what we have now

00:24:35.240 --> 00:24:39.590
into a full-blown service earning
